price too low to be resisted by any prospective mobile phone user. <img class="size-full wp-image-1366571 aligncenter" src="https://i2.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC09745.jpg?resize=6000%2C3376&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="6000" height="3376" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Zzapo Mobile has its corporate headquarters in London with corporate offices in Mauritius, Lagos while it boasts of a manufacturing unit in Shenzhen, China. Zzapo mobile phone features

